query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('cabal',
'deep-copy',
'filesystemwatcher',
'getter-setter',
'gunicorn',
'htmlunit',
'selenium-grid',
'shared',
'shortcode',
'streamwriter',
'text-processing',
'x509certificate');
